comments: Capela (ATL) briefly has a hand placed on George (UTA) before legally contesting the driving shot attempt.
Krejci (ATL) never fully establishes himself in a screening position, but the leg contact with George (UTA) is marginal.
Hunter (ATL) turns slightly after setting the pick on George (UTA) and marginal contact occurs.
Murray (ATL) extends his leg and creates any marginal contact with Collins (UTA) upon returning to the floor during the jump shot attempt.
Sexton (UTA) maintains his pivot foot at the end of his drive to the basket.
Sensabaugh (UTA) legally contests Murray's (ATL) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Juzang (UTA) makes incidental contact with Johnson's (ATL) hand on the ball during rebounding.
Krejci (ATL) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Capela (ATL) legally contests George's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
Sensabaugh (UTA) extends his arms into Johnson (ATL) slightly, who then trips over Collins' (UTA) foot.  The incidental contact causes Johnson to fall to the floor.
After communicating with the Replay Center, it is confirmed that George's (UTA) shot attempt does not make contact with the rim and the shot clock expires.
